  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to ascertain whether Arotinolol Hydrochloride reduces mortality
      and cardiovascular events in chronic kidney disease stage 5 patients with hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
